text: are bhai sharma kaise ho......ek toh tum yeh naam badal ke single A karwa lo phir tum bhi Ayush club ke hissa ban jaoge....apni mulaqat yuhi random hui thi jitna mujhe yaad hai...bas library mai aate jaate smile exchange karna...phir toh ek group ka atoot hissa hi ban gaye.... assignment notes jugaadne ke liye shukriya....woh code mangwana assignment jugaadna scientific computing II toh tumne hi paar karaya hai.....kam time par quality time spend hua tumhare saath...woh bbq ke din chal ke jaana mera alag ho jana tumhara call aana...kaafi kuch yaad aa gaya achanak se yeh likhte likhte...anyways koshish rahegi jald milne ki...wish you all the best aur ummed karte hai aap jeevan mai aise hi chapte rahe aur enjoy karte rahe

text: aur bhai abhijaat kaise ho....apni mulaqat kaise hui yeh toh abhi yaad nahi par andaza lagaya ja sakta hai (via goel aur jd)...phir toh wo goel ke room pe discussion....mlsp pe maje lena...kaafi kuch saath mil gaya....uske baad toh mafia business wo toh pura semester hi maje mai beeth gaya....intern placement prep bhi yaad hai...katai chaapu ho tum..ab tum cpi ka comparison nahi karna...all in all kaafi chill + chapu person..wish u all the best...#MultiTalented #Unique #CoderGraphQuestion....ummed karte hai jald milne ki....

text: Oho sonty boi kaise ho....suna toh tha tumhare baare mai par mulaqat late hui...par jab hui tab se lekar ab tak kaafi achi rahi....pehle laga ki tum toh dassa boi hoge phir jana toh pata laga ki tum toh humare jaise ho jo ek hafta pehle sab kuch suru karta :')....kaafi chill rehte waise toh tum but end sem aate hi ek dum serious...woh apna shiru jana...mere room pe ds ka assignment banana...woh bbq wali treat...yaad rahengi yeh mujhe... online sem mai answer jugaadne ke liye shukriya....is mahine toh mulaqat nahi hui wing mai hi rehta tha mai but ummed hai ki jald hogi... tab tak ke liye good bye and all the best..jald milenge

text: aur bhai gang-war kaise ho....ek dum chaapu aadmi always serious but sometimes participate in fun activities....kabhi mafia nahi khela yaar tumhare saath...sab aate the kotamkar goel ek tum hi reh jaate the.....humare mlsp ke chintan ke liye shukriya.....mujhe sirf tumhara expected tha day 1 placement(sach mai)..lol....khair usse kya 62lpa ctc ja rahe toh badhiya hi hai...aise hi sincere disciplined bane raho aaage jaoge...but dosto ko mat bhul jaaya karo..tumhari treat ab tak pending hai :)...anyways..kaafi acha raha tumko jaanke..kayi cheezo ke perspective hi badal diye ;')...all the best for future..location alag hai warna toh job ke time mil lete par koi na ummed hai ki jald milenge....

text:
aur bhai nareda kaise ho...tumhara memoir socha tha pehle likhne ka par free aaj hua aur fursat mai likhna tha....kaafi sara hoga waise likhne ka so aalas....anyway here it is....tumhe pehle jana tha toh pata chala ki chillness knows no boundaries....pehli identity - gamer, ameer, chilled guy.....phir second year se toh tum ek dum mere bakchodi partner ban gaye...kahi bhi jana tumhara saath kuch bhi kaam nahi toh aa gaye tumhara room bahut bakchodi ki hai bhai kitni ginaye...wo saath mai hunter hunter phir 12:00 se 12:02 tak happy new year...wo delhi ka safar bus se (adventure with death)...woh bombay ki trip...kaafi saath raha hai second sem se hi...saath mai canteen jana tumhara paiso pe :'), beete mahine bhi bas hum dono hi the jo har waqt free rehte the tumhara saath rehte rehte mai bhi free ho gaya....baaki goa trip pe na aane ka dukh hai par koi na ummed hai ki aage aur bhi trips saath mai hongi...likhte likhte mujhe abhi porn discussion at sahil room yaad aa gya :), bhai bahut time saath gujara hai maja aaya milte rehna #AllTheBest #Bhai #BakchodiPartner
Keep in mind - you are a bad boi doing bad things....aur kya likhe...ek achi baat - tu judge nahi karta logo ko aur karta hai toh maje mai uda deta hai #Relatable....ab toh apna bhai bhi bandi wala ho gaya...#MeALoner....Anyways, likhe likhte kaafi incidents recall hue wo vikram ki trip cawnpore mai paisa wo ghumta hua hotel..aise toh khatam nahi hongi par that was a good time..#WellSpentDays
Milte hai kabhi jab bhi yeh covid restriction hate..baaki koi trip ka plan bane toh batayeiga zaroor
author: Ayush  Shrotriya

text: ohoooo goel buddy kaise ho....mulaqt toh first year mai hi ho gayi thi par ache se jana tumko third sem se leke....phir toh college mai jidhar rahe tumko saath leke gaye...dept ke courses mai saath marwana khaali time mai mera tumhare room pe pade rehna...saath class jaana....placement ke tests....yaha tak ki fourth year ke courses bhi same :)..you are a good person filled with chapuness..kaise kar lete ho itna..trip toh nahi hui tumhare saath treat bhi kam hi hai wo bbq wali ko chodke par anyways kaafi time spend kiya humne saath mai...waise chance toh kam hai par ummed karte hai ki bangalore hi ho mera bhi toh saath maje karenge....kaash tum iss ek mahine college aate toh phir saath enjoy karte college ke aakhiri pal....waise mera kehna doesn't matter but I know you will achieve great things in your life...uske liye all the best...enjoy
author: Ayush  Shrotriya

text: aur bhai jain kaise ho.....likhna suru kar raha hu toh woh dept ke courses ki bt library mai end moment pe padhayi yaad aa ja rha hai...summer mai mera tumhare room pe aa jana apni life ki bt discuss karna tumko midsem end sem mai zyada padhne se rokna...phir bhi sitara le aaye tum.......all in all kaafi fun aaya tumhare saath..woh bbq wali treat aur uske bahar tempo ke pass tumhara sutta phukna yaad rahega...anyways kaafi chill person chapu bahut fields mai..acads decent hall captain galaxy photu..wagerah wagerah...abhi toh paisa kamao hilabs ko looto.....all the best for future...aasha karte hai aapke sapne poore ho + jald hi mulaqat ho...iss ek mahine aaye nahi tum warna ek treat toh ho hi jaati par koi na.....jald milenge

text: hello Dhawal boi....mulaqat apni thodi late hui but hui toh kaafi interesting rahi yeh journey....mile the tab hi lag gaya tha ki yeh different hai..bhai jab sabki phati rehti thi courses toh tu literally us time text book se padh raha hota tha...wo sitara 201 ka mai kaafi surprise hua tha sahi mai...ki humare beech koi itna chapu bhi hai...phir jab tumne bataya ki placement mai nahi baith rahe tab bhi surprise hua...par tum jo kar rahe uske liye kaafi himmat chhaiye and i wish you all the best for it...bharosa hai tum pe....kaafi unique personality hai tumhari so be yourself and though i want to say do not change...changes do come...hope these changes will bring the best of you....dept mai toh almost poora time mera tum logo ke saath hi gujra...yaha tak ki end sem baad bhi apan saath hi the 403 ka end sem....iss ek mahine zyada baat nahi hui par hi hello chalti rehti thi..wo smile exchange lol....hope to see you soon...all the best and aise hi chapte rehna

text: aur bhai karan kaise ho...tum un kuch chuninda laundo mai se ho jinmein humne badlav aate dekha hai..acha badlav....apan toh bhai the united in the hatred of s****i...but ek cheez same rahi tumme kaafi chillax type rahe humesha..iss ek mahine toh matlab ultimate..chapu toh tum ho hi #MLGod...saath mai canteen jana nareda ke paise pe...aur log kehte hai mai nareda ko loot raha :)...khair yaar trip nahi ho payi tumhare saath dono hi..uss baat ka dukh hai par aasha karte hai ki jald hi milenge gujju bhai...#AndhaPaisa #Chapu

text: waise toh tum wingie the par dhang se mulakat tumse galaxy mai hui....laga kya hum mai se kuch log itna acha bhi soch sakte...itne naye perspective....tab se laga yaar ki jab bhi gyaan ki dhara chhaiye hogi bas you are the person to contact...kabhi chochak ki leni hogi you are the person to reach...baaki yaar tum baiththe nahi ho bulla session wagerah mai...iss baar yeh ek mahine mai socha loki ko bhi rakhenge zabardasti bulake par yeh dosa ka ek mail...khair....best of luck for jo bhi tum aage ka socha jo ki tumne bataya ki abhi fix nahi.....milne ka vaada hai bas tum aa jana...

text: hello warrior panda..khan saheb..ummed karte hai yeh memoir padhte waqt aap swasth honge...jitna mujhe yaad hai apni mulaqat kaafi jaldi ho gayi thi...wajah same batch #PHY103...par ache se baat cheet suru hui jab tum b bot mai aaye...wajah bengali ke saath khidki pe ladayi...bhai kuch bhi kaho b bot ki bakchodi alag level pe thi ek se badhkar ek room...phir toh galaxy mai toh buddy ho gaye the wo saath hall ghumna bache leke aana saman lene jana poster pe like bhadwana aur bhi bahut kuch...phir toh hum bhi hab ke part ho gaye...par yeh sahil bhai ki hi meharbani thi ki kuch kaam nahi karna pada..sambhal lete hai humare bhaijaan...it was nice knowing you and working with you..achi baat ki tum kaafi straight forward ho jo baat hai bol di...buri baat kaafi diplomatic ho..waise its not that bad....ab aate hai iss ek mahine ke safar pe..bhai wo subah saath daudne jaana...pattte khelna...leather ball se beamer phekna....kaafi bakchodi peli saath mai aur ummed karte hai aage bhi kuch aise pal rahenge...baaki all the best for your dreams..waise tum achieve kar hi loge...dekha hai tumko ek hafte mai syllabus cover karte hue aur wo bhi ache seand not many people can do that #CATAspirant #SahilTheIITian..baaki trend ko zaari rakhte hue...#NotMyPresident :)

text: aur bhai lolu kaise ho......apni dosti toh suru mai hi ho gayi thi...yaad hai pehle midsem break mai tum aur mai bas do hi log the...gaali na dena unse uncomfortable hona phir chochak dildo ki sangat mai aake in cheezo ki uchaiyan chu lena...bahut progress ki tumne....yaar mereko ek baat humesha lagti hai ki tu tere mamlo mai kaafi panauti hai, kaafi incidents dekhe aur sune bhi par ek mast baat hai kaafi hard working ho jata hai tu agar man bana le toh...fattu hai par kaam kar leta hai and that is a very good thing...treat wagerah mai toh tum second year tak kam hi aate the...par bhai galaxy dono years ki...second year mai tum hi ignition laaye the aur mere liye toh ek supporting dependable role nibha rahe the...canteen mai baithna dosa khana kya din the...iss ek mahine bhi tumhara cooler hi humari jaan tha hume apne kamre mai sulane ke liye dhanyvad....apna toh college ka end bhi saath hi hua saath hi aaye car mai...kaafi acha raha safar tumko janke..ummed karte hai jald hi mulaqat hogi...abhi toh hilabs ko luto...#PanautiKismat

text: oho the chapu nana...kaise kar lete ho itni bakchodi..kya kuch nahi kiya tumne...dance kar liya drams kar liya bandi pata li..bas apne dosto ko party dena bhool gaya..last ke year mai na sahi par suru ke do saal toh khoob saath raha..woh tumhara antaragi ki practice se aana mere bed pe so jana..aalsi sala..galaxy mai tumhare charche...flow sunte sunte so jana.....tumhari bandi ka f*** **f bolna....apni toh treat bhi kaafi saath rahi suru mai...iss ek mahine toh mulaqat nahi aayi shayad tumne zaroori na samjha is dost se milna par hum ummed karte hai ki jald milenge aur tum se treat nikalwayenge..tab tak ke liye a goodbye...#TheRealChapu

text: apni pehli mulaqat pehle sem mai hui thi...kaise yaad nahi par tabse third year tak kaafi saath raha hai aur beete mahine mai bhi...ek dum mast aadmi ho tum chup chup ke offer letter likhna kisi ko nahi batana baad mai reveal karke lime light mai aa jana mere bed pe so jana......intern season mai mujhe bardast karne ke liye shukriya..mujhe tum humesha se long term thinker lage in terms of life achi baat hai ummed karte hai aapke bhi sapne poore ho...incidents toh yaad nahi aa rahe is samay par tumhara mujh ko padhana apna 2 baje doaa canteen is mahine subah tumhara na uth pana akele daudne chale jana kaafi kuch enjoyable moments rahe aur ummed karte hai ki aage bhi honge #AllTheBestForLife #ChupaRustom #TalentedBoi #DelhiSwag
author: Ayush  Shrotriya

text: aur bhai ramola kaise ho...dhang se baat toh kaafi time se nahi hui par jo bond suru mai bana tha wo aaj bhi barkaraar hai....jab mai aaya tha toh bahut cheezo se anjaan tha tab tum mile aur mera path pradarsith kiya like a guru....thanks for that...a sincere but fun loving guy....kaam ke time serious....mai fraudy tha toh tumse daant khata tha :).....lekin wo suru ke ek dedh saal kaafi fun aaya...kya bolte usko...ha..time spent well...calculating age difference b/w us....tumhara khade khade sona yaad hai.....books ka matter sort karwane ke liye shukriya...treat kaafi time se nahi hui tumhare saath + trip toh hui hi nahi...aane wale time mai jald milenge..kabhi ghar aane ka invitation ghumenge...saath pahad ghumenge aur vlog banayenge....tab tak ke liye good bye and all the best for future...you were and are my big bro thanks for everything man....jald milenge
author: Ayush  Shrotriya

text: aur bhai chochak kaise ho....first year ke pehle din se kaafi baatcheet hone lagi thi apni toh..saath mai mess jaana y15 ka apne room pe aake tumse shayari likhwana...aur phir first year mai toh dram mai bhi saath hi the...jab pehli baar pata chala ki tum bade wale nashedi ho toh kya judge kiya tha...par wo baatein ab peeche reh gayi :)...kaafi moody hua karte the tum lekin samay ke saath tumhe badalte dekha ek awastha mai rehte dekha....acha laga..iss ek mahine toh tumhara room hi mera B Mid ka aashiyana tha...memories toh is mahine hi bahut bana di jaisi ki tumhari height naapna tumhare paise ki chai peena aur bhi kayi baatein hai....par badla nikal hi liya tumne mujhe covid dekar...koi na maaf kiya tumhe...kabhi jaipur aao ghumne ke irade se toh batana milne ka plan karenge..upsc ke liye all the best...#DaughterYouHaveGrownSoMuch
author: Ayush  Shrotriya

text: waise tumhari wing ko toh mai pehle hi jaan chuka tha wajah goel aur shukla...par tum se ache se mulakat hui intern wale sem mai...laga tum toh hum jaise hi ho except ki thode zyada chapu ho....phir toh goel ke room pe tumse kotamkar se mulakat hone hi lag gayi thi....bhai wo placement ke calls mai kabhi nahi bhulunga :)...yeh sawal tum karo yeh mai karta hu yeh goel karega....khair abhi toh mulaqat ho nahi payi ache se par bangalore mai milte hai pakka se bas tum bhul na jana, tumhare pass waqt kidhar hoga...

text: Oho bhai parshad/paro kaise ho.....first impression of yours...kaafi cool hai yeh banda and i mean it....always calm quite supportive and a fun person to be with...mth mai ek saal aur rehna hai tumhe toh...kaafi himmat chhaiye lol...wo bbq wali treat ke liye shukriya mujhe yaad hai tum hi suru mai push kar rahe the....wo 403 ke endsem ke baad ki CCD treat bhi kaafi enjoy kari...that was a good time...anyways...hope to meet you soon gujju bhai...best of luck for future endeavours..

text: aur bhai arya kaise ho...ummed karte hai ki yeh padhte waqt swasth hoge....kaha se suru karein..second year kyuki first year mai toh jante hi nahi the :')....mera dept ka time toh lagbag poora apne group ke saath hi beeta hai..wo courses ki bt, end moment pe notes photocopy..palat ke wo samay dekhta hu toh dosti ke kaafi pal yaad aa jate...woh apna shiru jana..without sonty with sonty ki border line doondhna...anyways...kaafi chill kind of person and a proper engineer without a degree(BS)..saari cheez end moment pe hi khatam karte deadline se kuch samay pehle...apni treat toh ho gayi wo bbq wali ek trip ka plan bacha hai..aasha karte hai woh bhi jald pura hoga...kaash tum oracle aate phir udhar bhi saath enjoy karte..koi na jaha bhi raho chill karo enjoy karo....jald milenge

text: are bhai suppu....apan toh dram eve mai saath hi the toh jaan gaye the...pehle mujhe laga ki tum ajeeb insaan ho...phir dheere dheere samajh aaya ki oh tum toh insights different perspective wale aadmi ho...tumhari liye us din izzat badh gayi..dukh is baat ka hai ki tumse kabhi gyaan nahi le paaya..shukla loki dono se le liya...tumhe is ek mahine aana chhaiye tha campus par koi na....aasha karte hai ki tumse jald milenge aur sunnenge tumhari story..jao aur reserach karo aur noble leke aao...aur apni life enjoy karo...jald milenge

text: aur bhai tg kaise ho...pehle toh uss photu ke liye dil se shukriya.....iske baad....nayi job ke liye badhayi....iske baad advice...bandi aati jaati rahengi ab toh paisa bhi aa gaya bt mai pade rehna is never good humare saath enjoy karo....phir iske baad.....kaafi fun loving person to say but it all depends on your mood which i don't know is a good thing or bad thing :)....kaha se suru karein...waise jaane toh tumko late the par bhi enjoy kaafi kiya...woh intern prep ke time mt jaana tumhare paiso ki chai peena...intern na lagne ki bt saath khana...phi apan teeno ki lag jaane ke baad oat ki terrace pe life ka meaning search karna....tumhare ghar nahi aa paya yaar diwali pe aur tum bhi bulane nahi aaye is baat ka dukh hai....tumhara mujhe placement prep ke liye motivate karna(gaand phadne wala tareeka)....kaafi memories banayi...aur phir memories ka pitara galaxy ko toh kaise hi bhul sakte...photu club ko sambhalne ke liye shukriya mr. udgosh manager....iss ek mahine bhi kaafi saath raha..wo tumhara beamer phekna...bc sar pe lag jaye ball toh mar sakta aadmi....phir mera tumhara maje lena..waise mujhe malum nahi tha ki tum gussa ho gaye iske liye sorry..par bt mai pade rehna is not good..ab toh bhai ke pass gold hai crypto curr hai andha paisa hai toh ghar ke bahar line lag jayegi.....anyways that was a good time....aasha karte hai aapke sapne poore ho...life ke liye all the best....ummed karte hai ki jald milenge tum treat doge aur ghar bula loge....until next time..
author: Ayush  Shrotriya

text: are bhai vipul....apan the toh bhai par asli maja second year se kiya...b bot mai ek alag hi maja tha..wo bahar dhoop mai baithna..saath pubg khelna...wo omegle wali chat yaad hai tumhe...ab toh tum bhi bandi wale ho gaye #From12To2.....bas thoda padhle degree khatam kar placement lag jayegi thodi mehnat karega toh..aasha karte hai jald hi tumhari bhi ek post hogi jismein #AndhaPaisa likha hoga....apna toh kaafi time saath raha hai...third year mai bhi lolu aur tumhare room pe mera pade rehna...iss ek mahina wo daudne jana khelne jana tumhara chipkali bhagana..uske liye shukriya....ummed karte hai ki aapke sapne poore ho + aise hi chill raha karo(kuch matters pe thoda serious hona buri baat nahi)....jald milenge

text:
hello yatin...bsbe....boobies...kaise ho...kaha se suru karein...second year se karte hai..first year mai toh zyada ache se nahi janta tha..bagal wala room tumhare wo chutiyape aaj bhi smile le aate hai...summer mai tumhare room pe patte khelna...khud korean dekhkar tumhe spoiler dena...bsdk band karde korean dekhna...tumhare saath ladayi...haath mai sariya ghusne ke liye sorry...pehle mujhe kuch random points pe feel hota tha ki tumhare maje nahi lene chhaiye par mai jaise hi tumhari side leta tha tum hug dete the...but all in all kaafi innocent ho aisa kaha ja sakta hai...aur bsdk dusro ko khilana suru kar do..35 lakh logo ka ctc nahi hota tumhara income tax hai......realize karo bsbe ki tum ande ameer ho....iss ek mahine toh itni zyada mulaqat nahi hui..hui par kam...hall bhi alag aur late bhi aaye tum...par tumko jaanke maja aaya in chaar saalo mai...aage ki life ke liye all the best...ummed karta hu ki tum kabhi hume apne ghar bulaoge governor ke ghar chai ke liye leke jaoge :)...#BeakerGod....#BSBELegend...#AndaAmeer...
Tum bas investment karna seekh lo tumhe koi job nahi karni padegi...bahut paisa hai ghar mai...saara apne chote bhai ko le jaane de doge kya?
